description: Demolition of existing warehouse building (9,625 sq.m.) and the construction of part 2, part 3, part 4, part 5 and part 6 storey buildings comprising 20 houses (17x3-beds and 3x4-beds), 189 flats (81x1-beds; 80x2-beds and 28x3-beds), 3 live/work units (2-beds), car-parking for 160 vehicles, 234 cycle spaces and associated access and landscaping.
